<subSubSection id="C31343D2FFCAFFAF6180FAECC4F9F9D4" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB61059FFCAFFAF6180FAECC4F9F9D4" blockId="6.[151,1437,1194,1617]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6180FAECC46FFAD1" bold="true" box="[199,308,1338,1364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">Remarks</emphasis>
. The present species belongs to the 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF6393FAECC6BFFAD1" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1992" box="[724,996,1338,1364]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temaeus">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6393FAECC6BFFAD1" box="[724,996,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">Copidognathus temaeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group (
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF6579FAECC182FAD1" author="Bartsch, I." box="[1086,1241,1338,1364]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="231 - 243" refId="ref8699" refString="Bartsch, I. (1997) Copidognathinae (Halacaridae, Acari) from northern Australia; description of four new species. In: Hanley, J. R., Caswell, G., Megirian, D. &amp; Larson, H. K. (Eds.), Proceedings of the Sixth International Biological Workshop. Museums &amp; Art Galleries of Northern Territory, Darwin, pp. 231 - 243." type="book chapter" year="1997">Bartsch 1997</bibRefCitation>
; Chatterjee 
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6425FAEDC0CEFAD1" box="[1378,1429,1338,1364]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">et al</emphasis>
. 2006). Main characteristics of 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF60ABFA89C713FAFD" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1992" box="[492,584,1375,1400]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temaeus">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF60ABFA89C713FAFD" box="[492,584,1375,1400]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">temaeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group are: palps short, hardly surpassing the rostrum; Palpal segment 2 with spinular lamella; telofemur I often with spinular ventral lamella; tibia I with 2 blunt spurs with spinose tips (
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF6402FA54C588FA45" author="Bartsch, I." pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="231 - 243" refId="ref8699" refString="Bartsch, I. (1997) Copidognathinae (Halacaridae, Acari) from northern Australia; description of four new species. In: Hanley, J. R., Caswell, G., Megirian, D. &amp; Larson, H. K. (Eds.), Proceedings of the Sixth International Biological Workshop. Museums &amp; Art Galleries of Northern Territory, Darwin, pp. 231 - 243." type="book chapter" year="1997">Bartsch 1997</bibRefCitation>
). Four species are known in ‘ 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF6360FA71C7FDFA45" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1992" box="[551,678,1447,1473]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temaeus">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6360FA71C7FDFA45" box="[551,678,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">C. temaeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group’ so far: 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF6216FA71C175FA45" authority="Bartsch" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1992" box="[849,1070,1446,1473]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="temaeus">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6216FA71C694FA45" box="[849,975,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">C. temaeus</emphasis>
Bartsch
</taxonomicName>
from Moorea, Bora Bora, Society Islands, western Pacific and Andaman Islands, Indian Ocean (
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF62C3FA1CC177FA61" author="Bartsch, I." box="[900,1068,1482,1508]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="465 - 488" refId="ref8594" refString="Bartsch, I. (1992 a) Halacariden von den Inseln Moorea und Bora Bora, Gesellschaftsinseln (Arachnida: Acari). Senckenbergiana Biologica, 72, 465 - 488." type="journal article" year="1992">Bartsch 1992a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF657EFA1CC1A6FA60" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[1081,1277,1482,1509]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="141 - 143" refId="ref10100" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1996 a) Record of Copidognathus temaeus Bartsch (Halacaridae: Acari) from Indian Ocean. Journal of the Marine Biological Association of India, 38 (1 &amp; 2), 141 - 143." type="journal article" year="1996">Chatterjee 1996a</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF6454FA1CC46DF98D" authority="Bartsch, 1993" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1993" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malaysius">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6454FA1CC0C6FA61" box="[1299,1437,1482,1508]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">C.malaysius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF61D0FA38C46DF98D" author="Bartsch, I." box="[151,310,1518,1544]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="45 - 58" refId="ref8663" refString="Bartsch, I. (1993) Halacaridae (Acari) von Malaysia. Beschreibung von drei Arten der Gattung Copidognathus. Entomologische Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Hamburg, 11, 45 - 58." type="journal article" year="1993">Bartsch, 1993</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from Archipelago Tioman, eastern coast of 
<collectingCountry id="F31E50C9FFCAFFAF6271FA38C6C6F98D" box="[822,925,1518,1544]" name="Malaysia" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF62E9FA38C111F98D" author="Bartsch, I." box="[942,1098,1518,1544]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="45 - 58" refId="ref8663" refString="Bartsch, I. (1993) Halacaridae (Acari) von Malaysia. Beschreibung von drei Arten der Gattung Copidognathus. Entomologische Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum Hamburg, 11, 45 - 58." type="journal article" year="1993">Bartsch 1993</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF6526FA39C0C7F98D" authority="Bartsch 1997" authorityName="Bartsch" authorityYear="1997" box="[1121,1436,1518,1545]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="elaborates">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF6526FA39C1A0F98D" box="[1121,1275,1518,1545]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">C. elaborates</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF6442FA38C0C7F98D" author="Bartsch, I." box="[1285,1436,1518,1544]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="231 - 243" refId="ref8699" refString="Bartsch, I. (1997) Copidognathinae (Halacaridae, Acari) from northern Australia; description of four new species. In: Hanley, J. R., Caswell, G., Megirian, D. &amp; Larson, H. K. (Eds.), Proceedings of the Sixth International Biological Workshop. Museums &amp; Art Galleries of Northern Territory, Darwin, pp. 231 - 243." type="book chapter" year="1997">Bartsch 1997</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from northern 
<collectingCountry id="F31E50C9FFCAFFAF6007F9C4C4FCF9A9" box="[320,423,1554,1580]" name="Australia" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">Australia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF60FFF9C4C708F9A9" author="Bartsch, I." box="[440,595,1554,1580]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="231 - 243" refId="ref8699" refString="Bartsch, I. (1997) Copidognathinae (Halacaridae, Acari) from northern Australia; description of four new species. In: Hanley, J. R., Caswell, G., Megirian, D. &amp; Larson, H. K. (Eds.), Proceedings of the Sixth International Biological Workshop. Museums &amp; Art Galleries of Northern Territory, Darwin, pp. 231 - 243." type="book chapter" year="1997">Bartsch 1997</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFCAFFAF63DFF9C5C19AF9A9" authority="Chatterjee, De Troch &amp; Chang 2006" authorityName="Chatterjee, De Troch &amp; Chang" authorityYear="2006" box="[664,1217,1554,1581]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fungiae">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF63DFF9C5C64BF9A9" box="[664,784,1554,1581]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">C. fungiae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFCAFFAF625DF9C4C19AF9A9" author="Chatterjee, T. &amp; De Troch, M. &amp; Chang, C. Y." box="[794,1217,1554,1581]" pageId="6" pageNumber="307" pagination="177 - 187" refId="ref11786" refString="Chatterjee, T., De Troch, M. &amp; Chang, C. Y. (2006) Three halacarid mites of the genus Copidognathus (Acari: Halacaridae) from Zanzibar, Tanzania. Cahiers de Biologie Marine, 47, 177 - 187." type="journal article" year="2006">Chatterjee, De Troch &amp; Chang 2006</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F31E50C9FFCAFFAF644BF9C4C0C7F9A8" box="[1292,1436,1554,1581]" name="South Korea" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">South Korea</collectingCountry>
(Chatterjee 
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFCAFFAF605CF9E1C417F9D5" box="[283,332,1590,1616]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="307">et al</emphasis>
. 2006).
